# Package manager caches
# REF-3: workspaces hoist to the root lockfile — nested lockfiles caused version
# drift / non-reproducible installs. Keep only the root package-lock.json.
# EXCEPTION (2026-07): frontend/package-lock.json is committed — the frontend
# Docker build context can't see the root lockfile, and `npm ci` needs it so
# the production image builds the exact dependency tree that was tested
# (regenerate via `npm install --package-lock-only` on a copied package.json,
# NOT inside the workspace).
backend/package-lock.json
.npm/
.pnpm-store/
.yarn/cache/
.yarn/unplugged/
.yarn/build-state.yml
.yarn/install-state.gz

